name: Retrieve current config details
xml: <get-resource plugin='org.onap.ccsdk.sli.adaptors.resource.sql.SqlResource' resource='SQL' key="SELECT service_description, vnf_name, vm_name, vnf_type, vnfc_type, host_ip_address , content FROM UPLOAD_CONFIG WHERE vnf_id = $input.action-identifiers.vnf-id AND config_indicator='Current' AND (pending_delete IS NULL OR pending_delete != 'Y')" pfx="currnt-config[]">

name: return failure
xml:
<return status='failure'>
<parameter name='error-code' value='401'/>
<parameter name='error-message' value="`$error-message`"/>
<parameter name='output.status.code' value='401'/>
<parameter name='output.status.message' value="`$error-message`"/>

name: Set error message
xml:
<set>
<parameter name='error-message' value="`'Current configuration not found in the repository for vnf-id: ' + $input.action-identifiers.vnf-id`"/>

name: Set error message
xml:
<set>
<parameter name='error-message' value="`'Error while retrieving current configuration from the repository for the vnf-id: ' + $input.action-identifiers.vnf-id`"/>

name: Set context
xml:
<set>
<parameter name='service-description' value="`$currnt-config[$i].service-description`" />
<parameter name='vm-name' value="`$currnt-config[$i].vm-name`" />
<parameter name='vnf-type' value="`$currnt-config[$i].vnf-type`" />
<parameter name='vnfc-type' value="`$currnt-config[$i].vnfc-type`" />
<parameter name='host-ip-address' value="`$currnt-config[$i].host-ip-address`" />
<parameter name='vnf-name' value="`$currnt-config[$i].vnf-name`" />
<parameter name='current-config' value="`$currnt-config[$i].content`" />

name: Set error message
xml:
<set>
<parameter name='error-message' value='DG to retrieve running configuration not found'/>

name: return failure
xml:
<return status='failure'>
<parameter name='error-code' value='401'/>
<parameter name='error-message' value="`$error-message`"/>
<parameter name='output.status.code' value='401'/>
<parameter name='output.status.message' value="`$error-message`"/>

name: Log error
xml:
<record plugin="onap.ccsdk.sli.core.sli.recording.Slf4jRecorder">
<parameter name="level" value="error"/>
<parameter name="logger" value="message-log"/>
<parameter name="record" value="`$error-message`"/>

name: Log error
xml:
<record plugin="onap.ccsdk.sli.core.sli.recording.Slf4jRecorder">
<parameter name="level" value="error"/>
<parameter name="logger" value="message-log"/>
<parameter name="record" value="`$error-message`"/>

name: Log message
xml:
<record plugin="onap.ccsdk.sli.core.sli.recording.Slf4jRecorder">
<parameter name="level" value="debug"/>
<parameter name="logger" value="message-log"/>
<parameter name="record" value="`'Retrieving current configuration details from the repository for vnf-id: ' + $input.action-identifiers.vnf-id`"/>

name: Log message
xml:
<record plugin="onap.ccsdk.sli.core.sli.recording.Slf4jRecorder">
<parameter name="level" value="debug"/>
<parameter name="logger" value="message-log"/>
<parameter name="record" value="`'Audit action successful for vnf-id: ' + $input.action-identifiers.vnf-id`"/>

name: Set error message
xml:
<set>
<parameter name='error-message' value="`'Error comparing current and running configuration for vnf-id: ' + $input.action-identifiers.vnf-id`"/>
<parameter name='error-code' value='500'/>

name: Log error
xml:
<record plugin="onap.ccsdk.sli.core.sli.recording.Slf4jRecorder">
<parameter name="level" value="error"/>
<parameter name="logger" value="message-log"/>
<parameter name="record" value="`$Error-Message`"/>

name: return failure
xml:
<return status='failure'>
<parameter name='error-code' value="`$error-code`"/>
<parameter name='error-message' value="`$error-message`"/>
<parameter name='output.status.code' value='401'/>
<parameter name='output.status.message' value="`$error-message`"/>

name: Compare
xml:
<execute plugin='org.onap.sdnc.config.audit.node.CompareNode' method='compare' >
<parameter name='sourceDataType' value="Current" />
<parameter name='sourceData' value="`$current-config`" />
<parameter name='targetDataType' value="Running" />
<parameter name='targetData' value="`$running-config.content`" />
<parameter name='compareDataType' value="`$protocol`" />

name: Set error message
xml:
<set>
<parameter name='error-message' value="`'Running configuration not found in the repository for vnf-id: ' + $input.action-identifiers.vnf-id`"/>

name: Set error message
xml:
<set>
<parameter name='error-message' value="`'Error while retrieving running configuration from the repository for the vnf-id: ' + $input.action-identifiers.vnf-id`"/>

name: Retrieve Running config details DB
xml: <get-resource plugin='org.onap.ccsdk.sli.adaptors.resource.sql.SqlResource' resource='SQL' key=" SELECT upload_config_id, request_id, originator_id, service_description, action, upload_date, vnf_id, vnf_name, vm_name, vnf_type, vnfc_type, host_ip_address, config_indicator, pending_delete ,content FROM UPLOAD_CONFIG WHERE UPLOAD_CONFIG_ID = $runningConfig.UPLOAD-CONFIG-ID" pfx="running-config" >

name: Report error to DCAE
xml:
<execute plugin='org.onap.appc.dg.common.DCAEReporterPlugin' method='report' >
<parameter name="eventId" value="`$input.action-identifiers.vnf-id`" />
<parameter name="output.status.message" value="Failure while generating output payload JSON" />

<parameter name="output.status.message" value="Failure in flattening payload Json" />
